# ingredients
500|gram|sourdough discard
500|gram|milk
2||egg
80|gram|sugar
50|gram|flour
25|gram|oil
10|gram|baking soda
8|gram|salt

# instructions
Mix all ingredients.
Let mixture rest for 15 minutes.
Ladle onto a hot pan so the batter forms a thin film.
Wait for crepe to bubble then flip.
